css: .tooltip a, .dhx_cal_qi_content a {overflow-wrap: break-word;word-break: break-all; color: white; border-bottom: 1px solid #ffcd03; text-decoration: none; line-height: 25px;} .dhtmlXTooltip.tooltip {line-height: 30px;} .tooltip a:hover, .dhx_cal_qi_content a:hover  {background: #fff; color: #000003;} .dhx_cal_event_line {background: #FFCD03;} .dhx_cal_tab {color: #FFCD03; border: 1px solid #FFCD03;} .dhx_cal_tab.active {background: #FFCD03; color: black;} .dhx_cal_tab:hover {background: #FFCD03; color: black;} .dhx_cal_today_button {border: 1px solid #FFCD03; color: #FFCD03;} .dhx_cal_today_button:hover {background: #FFCD03; border: 1px solid #FFCD03;} .dhx_cal_event_clear::before, .dhx_cal_qi_tcontent::before {background: #FFCD03 ;} .dhx_qi_big_icon, .dhx_qi_big_icon:hover {color: #FFCD03;} .dhx_menu_icon {background-color: #FFCD03;} .details {overflow-wrap: break-word;word-break: break-all;} .dhtmlXTooltip {min-width: 250px; max-width: 450px;}
